{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerSmsNumber:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"number"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The phone number in E.164 international format.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"number"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Associates a phone number with the current device for SMS marketing campaigns.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This enables omnichannel messaging where users can receive communications via","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"both push notifications and SMS."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The phone number must be in E.164 international format:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Start with ‘+’ followed by country code","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No spaces, dashes, or parentheses"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Examples: “+14155551234” (US), “+447911123456” (UK), “+491711234567” (Germany)"}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Register SMS during phone verification flow:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class PhoneVerificationController {","","    func verifyPhoneNumber(_ phoneNumber: String, code: String,","                          completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.verifyCode(phone: phoneNumber, code: code) { [weak self] result in","            switch result {","            case .success:","                let normalizedNumber = self?.normalizeToE164(phoneNumber) ?? phoneNumber","                Pushwoosh.configure.registerSmsNumber(normalizedNumber)","","                Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                    \"phone_verified\": true,","                    \"sms_opted_in\": true,","                    \"phone_country\": self?.extractCountryCode(from: normalizedNumber) ?? \"\"","                ])","","                completion(.success(()))","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","","    private func normalizeToE164(_ phone: String) -> String {","        let digits = phone.components(separatedBy: CharacterSet.decimalDigits.inverted).joined()","        return phone.hasPrefix(\"+\") ? \"+\\(digits)\" : \"+1\\(digits)\"","    }","","    private func extractCountryCode(from e164: String) -> String {","        \/\/ Extract country code from E.164 format","        guard e164.hasPrefix(\"+\") else { return \"\" }","        let countryCodeLength = e164.count > 12 ? 2 : (e164.count > 11 ? 1 : 1)","        return String(e164.dropFirst().prefix(countryCodeLength))","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Registers an SMS number for SMS messaging campaigns.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"registerSmsNumber:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerSmsNumber:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerSmsNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerSmsNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerSmsNumber:"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registersmsnumber:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerSmsNumber:":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerSmsNumber:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerSmsNumber:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"registerSmsNumber:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"registerSmsNumber:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers an SMS number for SMS messaging campaigns."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registersmsnumber:","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}]}}}